<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM9.3.10">
<l>ilaṅku muttum pavaḷak koḻuntu meḻiltāmarai</l>
<l>pulaṅkaḷ muṟṟum poḻilcūḻn taḻakā yapullāṇimēl</l>
<l>kalaṅka lillāp pukaḻāṉ kaliya ṉolimālai</l>
<l>valaṅkoḷ toṇṭark kiṭamā vatupā ṭilvaikuntamē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>For those devotees who have the skill of [reciting this] garland of words</l>
<l>Of Kaliyaṉ, the one whose fame is fearlessness, about lovely Pullāṇi</l>
<l>Surrounded by groves [and] where bright pearls, coral branches,</l>
<l rend="indent">and colorful lotuses</l>
<l>Ripen in the fields, [their] place will be sorrow-free Vaikunta.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
